                    </div>
                    <hr class="separator" />
                    <div class="list">
                        <div class="row"><strong>Mode:</strong><span class="teacher-info">Online Live</span></div>
                        <div class="row"><strong>Certification:</strong><span class="teacher-info">Yes (On
