                    </div>
                </aside>
            </section>

            <!-- Main Content -->
            <main class="grid">
                <div>
                    <!-- Section 1 -->
                    <section class="section primary item-hover">
                        <h2>What you'll learn</h2>
                        <p>
                            By the end of this course, you’ll be able to collect, clean, and analyze data to build
                            predictive and classification models.
                            You’ll also learn how to evaluate and fine-tune models for real-world applications.
                        </p>
                        <div class="tag-container">
                            <div class="topics-column">
                                <h3>Core topics</h3>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Python for Machine Learning</li>
                                    <li>Data Preprocessing & Feature Engineering</li>
                                    <li>Supervised & Unsupervised Algorithms</li>
                                    <li>Model Evaluation & Validation</li>
                                    <li>Model Deployment Techniques</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="topics-column">
                                <h3>Hands-on</h3>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>10+ ML projects with real datasets</li>
                                    <li>Regression and classification model training</li>
                                    <li>Clustering and dimensionality reduction</li>
                                    <li>End-to-end deployment using Flask / Streamlit</li>
                                    <li>Capstone: Predictive analytics project</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <!-- Section 2 - Syllabus -->
