                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="left">
                                    <div class="module-num">01</div>
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="card-info-strong">Introduction to Machine Learning</div>
                                        <div class="card-info-small">Overview, applications & use cases</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div>+</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">Topics: What is ML, applications across industries, types of ML
