                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="left">
                                    <div class="module-num">02</div>
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="card-info-strong">Python for ML</div>
                                        <div class="card-info-small">Libraries & Data Handling</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div>+</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">Topics: NumPy, Pandas, Matplotlib, Seaborn, data cleaning, data
                                transformation and visualization.</div>

                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="left">
                                    <div class="module-num">03</div>
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="card-info-strong">Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)</div>
                                        <div class="card-info-small">Data Visualization & Insights</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div>+</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">Topics: Handling missing values, outliers, feature correlation, and
                                statistical summaries.</div>

                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="left">
                                    <div class="module-num">04</div>
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="card-info-strong">Supervised Learning</div>
                                        <div class="card-info-small">Regression & Classification Models</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div>+</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">Topics: Linear Regression, Logistic Regression, Decision Trees, Random
                                Forest, Gradient Boosting, SVM.</div>

                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="left">
                                    <div class="module-num">05</div>
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="card-info-strong">Unsupervised Learning</div>
                                        <div class="card-info-small">Clustering & Dimensionality Reduction</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div>+</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">Topics: K-Means, Hierarchical Clustering, PCA, t-SNE, anomaly
                                detection.</div>

                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="left">
                                    <div class="module-num">06</div>
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="card-info-strong">Model Evaluation & Optimization</div>
                                        <div class="card-info-small">Metrics & Hyperparameter Tuning</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div>+</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">Topics: Cross-validation, confusion matrix, ROC/AUC, GridSearchCV,
                                feature selection and scaling.</div>

                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="left">
                                    <div class="module-num">07</div>
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="card-info-strong">Advanced ML Concepts</div>
                                        <div class="card-info-small">Ensemble & Time Series Models</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div>+</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">Topics: Bagging, Boosting, Stacking, ARIMA, LSTM intro for forecasting.
                            </div>

                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="left">
                                    <div class="module-num">08</div>
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="card-info-strong">Model Deployment</div>
                                        <div class="card-info-small">Web Apps & Cloud Deployment</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div>+</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">Topics: Saving models with Pickle, Streamlit dashboards, Flask APIs,
